hopobject.body: Your cash is being counted kings medical clinic The number of staff making Burberry's signature raincoat at its British factory in Castleford, West Yorkshire, has been doubled since 2011 amid high demand, with sales of outerwear and large leather goods such as its Blaze and Orchard bags, accounting for half the brand's sales growth. Menswear sales rose 25% over the quarter as the label brought its men's catwalk show back to London this year.
